skills/README.md:52:### `close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs`\n../9104-56cf3305/skills/README.md:54:Closes batches of open pull requests that have the `human-intervention` label or failing CI.\n../9104-56cf3305/skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:2:name: close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs\n../9104-56cf3305/skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:3:description: Close batches of graalvm-reachability-metadata pull requests that either have the `human-intervention` label or failing CI, and revert their linked issues by clearing assignees and moving project status to `Todo`.\n../9104-56cf3305/skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:18:- The PR has the `human-intervention` label.\n../9104-56cf3305/skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:29:   - Fetch open human-intervention PRs:\n../9104-56cf3305/skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:31:     gh pr list -R oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata --state open --label human-intervention --limit 200 --json number,title,url,labels,statusCheckRollup\n../9104-56cf3305/skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:150:     gh pr close PR_NUMBER -R oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata --comment \"Closing this human-intervention PR and returning the linked issue to Todo.\"\n../9104-56cf3305/skills/close-human-intervention-and-failing-ci-prs/SKILL.md:183:- PRs closed for `human-intervention`\n../9102-2d18b920/stats/org.apache.httpcomponents.core5/httpcore5/5.2/execution-metrics.json:6:    \"ending_commit\": \"036f6cf8564a2d62fc19cd65168e32ac20d906d6\",\n../9102-5f94cbe9/stats/org.apache.httpcomponents.core5/httpcore5/5.2/execution-metrics.json:6:    \"ending_commit\": \"036f6cf8564a2d62fc19cd65168e32ac20d906d6\",\n../9104-56cf3305/stats/org.apache.httpcomponents.core5/httpcore5/5.2/execution-metrics.json:6:    \"ending_commit\": \"036f6cf8564a2d62fc19cd65168e32ac20d906d6\",\n../9102-2d18b920/stats/org